Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:23.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}於是牽住了夥伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:29.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}這樣的話將永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:34.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年無憂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:41.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論如何都想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:47.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夥伴們曾牽在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:54.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已變得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:58.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一個個漸漸離去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:05.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向著那甦醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:14.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}邁開腳步毅然前進
